quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  40,59,qayamat anay wali hai is mein kuch shak nahi. lekin aksar log imaan nahi rakhtay
  40,60,aur tumahray perwar-digaar ne kaha hai ke tum mujh se dua karo mein tumhari ( dua ) qubool karoon ga. jo log meri ibadat se Azrah taqqabur kanyatay hain. anqareeb jahannum mein zaleel ho kar daakhil hon ge
  40,61,khuda hi to hai jis ne tumahray liye raat banai ke is mein aaraam karo aur din ko roshan banaya ( ke is mein kaam karo ) be shak khuda logon par fazl karne wala hai. lekin aksar log shukar nahi karte
  40,62,yahi khuda tumhara perwar-digaar hai jo har cheez ka peda karne wala hai. is ke siwa koi mabood nahi phir tum kahan bhatak rahay ho ?
  40,63,isi terhan woh log bhatak rahay they jo khuda ki aayton se inkaar karte they
  40,64,khuda hi to hai jis ne zameen ko tumahray liye tehrnay ki jagah aur aasman ko chhat banaya aur tumhari soorten banayen aur soorten bhi khoob banayen aur tumhe pakeeza cheeze khanay ko den. yahi khuda tumhara perwar-digaar hai. pas khuday-e perwar-digaar aalam bohat hi babarkat hai
  40,65,woh zindah hai ( jisay mout nahi ) is ke siwa koi ibadat ke Laiq nahi to is ki ibadat ko khalis kar kar isi ko poukaro. har terhan ki tareef khuda hi ko ( sazawar ) hai jo tamam Jahan ka perwar-digaar hai
  40,66,( ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihiwasallam un se ) keh do ke mujhe is baat ki momanat ki gayi hai ke jin ko tum khuda ke siwa pkarte ho un ki parastish karoon ( aur mein un ki kyonkr parastish karoon ) jab ke mere paas mere perwar-digaar ( ki taraf ) se khuli daleelen aa chuki hain aur mujh ko yeh hukum howa hai ke perwar-digaar aalam hi ka tabay farmaan hon
